33:36.660 --> 33:41.048
from over there to come here. From Sunrise to the 
ranch. To build one in the ranch. She's talking

33:46.803 --> 33:50.329
about your boss, mom. Did you work with a boss? In 
Mexico? Yes, my husband did. What's the name of

33:56.880 --> 34:00.126
your husband's boss in Mexico? Do you remember? I 
