37:33.307 --> 37:33.568
Let's go. This girl who is in Pennsylvania, now 
that she came, we went two or three times to Laredo.

37:38.578 --> 37:40.763
And Juanita also took me to Mexico. And no... Ya de 
hora que nosotros tenemos carros, vamos pa' todas

37:42.648 --> 37:47.181
partes. Sí. Y ahora dice, ahora que me den las 
vacaciones, vamos pa' California. Le digo, pues

37:53.679 --> 37:55.645
sí, sí, vamos. That's why the thought, the person 
has it since they were little. When she was in low

38:03.408 --> 38:14.327
grade, all the time she would tell me, mom, when I 
grow up, let's say I'm a girl and I finish school and

38:03.408 --> 38:14.327
go to work. I'm going to buy a car, she would say, and 
then I'll take her everywhere for a walk, she would

38:14.387 --> 38:22.881
say. And I tell her, look, it seems that God granted 
you, because now that she finished her school, she

38:23.401 --> 38:45.612
then bought her first cart, and now she bought 
another cart, and she takes me everywhere,

38:23.401 --> 38:45.612
wherever I tell her to go, I just tell her... Get out 
of work and let's go. See? God granted us, He

38:51.571 --> 38:55.877
granted you to take us for a walk. Yes. Yes. Well, 
this is one of the most interesting stories I've

38:58.020 --> 39:05.311
heard. You've heard. Yes. And thank you very much. 
