39:35.901 --> 39:45.812
muchacho, mamá, usted debió de haber puesto en el 
papel, dijo, la historia de la vida de mi hermano. Y

39:45.832 --> 39:51.478
le dije, pues sí, pero como yo no sé leer, si yo 
supiera leer, cállate. Yo estoy, estoy, estoy,

39:52.199 --> 39:55.123
estoy de todo. Porque dice mi mamá que yo no sé por 
qué yo, mira, I bring money, I bring things like

40:01.799 --> 40:10.012
that, whatever I buy. I don't know where, so much 
that I raise it, I don't know where it is. And you see

40:14.359 --> 40:17.745
everything I've been telling you. And I have many 
more things. And how is it being recorded? How do I

40:25.357 --> 40:26.840
have all that? You see? Because as I told you 
before, that I, I had thoughts for my children and

40:36.106 --> 40:40.471
for my husband. Because the advice that I gave to my 
children, I gave them to my husband. But he never

40:47.199 --> 40:50.102
took them. He forgot them. And that's why I tell my 
mother, I tell her, if I lost, and I have lost my head

40:51.664 --> 41:02.637
since I got married, just like his, I wouldn't have 
had my children, I wouldn't have known about my

41:03.832 --> 41:08.637
children, I wouldn't have known about anything. 
But no. I thought that I had to take care of my

41:10.138 --> 41:16.825
children. Yes. And I had to, if not, well, I 
couldn't have. And that's what I tell him, and I

41:20.949 --> 41:31.459
always find out with my children, with my 
daughter, Why don't they raise their family like I

41:33.177 --> 41:39.687
raised them? Because it's very nice that they say, 
as always, that it's not that they appropriate me,

41:39.707 --> 41:55.511
but always the people where we have lived have been 
envious of my family. Why do I have what I have? ¿Por

42:01.004 --> 42:02.890
qué yo tengo carro? ¿Por qué yo esto? Porque 
trabajo y mis hijos trabajan igual a mí. Y yo ando

42:08.206 --> 42:11.335
con mis hijos. All together. If I wasn't going to 
work, I wasn't going to go to work alone. No. I

42:19.363 --> 42:20.244
rested my daughter too. I was going to work, she was 
going to go. I never admitted that. Not that I was

42:25.311 --> 42:30.478
going to church alone, not that I was going to go 
with anyone. All together, all together. An

42:33.982 --> 42:41.372
American lady told us when we got to work, we were 
going to get there and they said, grab so many

42:33.982 --> 42:41.372
surcos. And they would come and grab my boys, and if 
not me, I would grab them all. And the American lady

42:49.253 --> 42:53.927
would say, look, here comes the guajolata with the 
guajolotitos.

